The '''Zimbabwe Institution of Engineers''' is the [[professional organization]] of [[engineers]] in [[Zimbabwe]]. It has graded membership, including student, technician, graduate and corporate membership as well as the status of fellow.<ref>{{cite web|title=ZIE Categories of Memberships|url=http://www.zie.org.zw/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=51%3Azie-types-of-memberships&catid=25%3Athe-project&Itemid=53|publisher=ZIE|accessdate=1 April 2012}}</ref> 

